HEADWORD: Etherize
<hw>E"ther*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. &
p. p.</pos> <conjf>Etherized</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
